data.title: Futura Classic: Technical Data Sheet
data.meta_description: Futura - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This technical data sheet provides information on Futura Classic, a two-component chemically curing aliphatic acrylic polyurethane coating. It has a glossy finish and good gloss retention. It is intended for use as a topcoat on marine vessels and a wide range of industrial structures. Key information includes typical properties, surface preparation needed, application methods, drying times, and packaging details.
